AB  - This paper presents a closed form solution to the Amihud-Mendelson model that incorporates bid-ask spreads into the required rate of return on capital assets. Return premiums are shown to be concave in the cost of trading. Two types of liquid assets are defined; quoted and non-quoted, and the applicability of the model to the two types is discussed.
